data.description: Warm and cozy one story gem in the charming Escondido Meadows community, located within 15 minutes of JBSA Randolph! This home features durable ceramic tile and wood laminate flooring through the living areas and secondary bedrooms. The kitchen feature ample cabinet and counter space, built-in microwave, reverse osmosis water filtration system, recessed lights and the refrigerator is included! The spacious primary suite includes fresh carpet in the bedroom and walk-in closet. The primary bath boasts a double vanity and a separate tub and shower. Schedule your showing today!
